       pr_para4: "Privacy Notice",
       pr_para5: " is designed to help you understand what kind of Personal Data we collect via our Services (as defined below). We also explain what role we have in the processing of Personal Data, how long we retain Personal Data and what rights you have as a ",
       pr_para6: "Data Subject.",
       pr1_para: "Under the California Consumer Privacy Act ",
